
onion.py - Setup wizard:

 This is a setup wizard to configure and create your OnionMail
 on TAILS.
 
 1) Activate the persistance.
 2) Download this script
 3) Run via command line:
 ./onionmail.py
 
OnionMail is an open-source Hidden Mail Service
See http://onionmail.info for more info.

